These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, june, november, july
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, mauve, orange, fuchsia
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, indonesian, polish
House: tower, colonial, art-deco, farmhouse
1. the colombian is the person who likes fuchsia##1
2. the indonesian is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in july##2
3. the colombian is the tower house##1
4. the farmhouse house is on the left of the tower house##1
5. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the art-deco house is the person who's birthday is in november##1
7. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
8. the canadian is on the far right##1
9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Birthday   | june | july   | march  | november  |
| Color   | mauve    | fuchsia    | yellow      | orange    |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian | indonesian | canadian |
| House     | farmhouse  | tower       | colonial    | art-deco     |

