.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
There 4 different types of food: grapes, eggplant, plum, asparagus
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk, soy-milk, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, lawyer, designer, software-developer
1. the software-developer is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking water is the lawyer##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person eating asparagus is between the person drinking soy-milk and the social-worker##2
6. the software-developer is between the person eating asparagus and the person drinking water##2
7. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
8. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the person eating plum is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| Food   | grapes      | eggplant  | asparagus  | plum |
| Beverage           | water      | soy-milk       | almond-milk      | sprite       |
| Job         | lawyer    | software-developer | designer | social-worker |

