.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, lemon, mango
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, bluemaster, montecristo, bongani
4 different games are played: snooker, whist, bridge, monopoly
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, comedy, superhero, scientific
1. the person playing bridge is the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
6. the person playing whist is the bongani-smoker##1
7. the person eating mango is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
8. the person eating artichoke is between the aristoff-smoker and the bongani-smoker##2
9. the montecristo-smoker is between the person eating lemon and the person playing whist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | blueberry | lemon     | artichoke   | mango     |
| Cigar       | bluemaster   | aristoff   | montecristo | bongani |
| Game         | snooker   | bridge | monopoly       | whist    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero    | comedy | fantasy  | scientific    |

