.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, iris, tulip, aconite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, martial-arts, scientific
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, sprite, cola
City: liverpool, nizza, new-york, prague
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is the person who growsbellflower##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is the person who growstulip##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
10. the person who growsiris is between the person drinking mirinda and the person who growsaconite##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Flower           | bellflower  | aconite | iris     | tulip |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action  | martial-arts | disaster       |
| Beverage           | iced-tea       | cola    | sprite      | mirinda           |
| City         | liverpool | nizza   | prague   | new-york         |

