.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, bus, quad-bike, train
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, lawyer, security-guard, social-worker
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, vegafina, alhambra, dannemann
House: farmhouse, tower, wooden, townhouse
 1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 2. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
 3. the security-guard is the person driving the bus##1
 4. the security-guard is on the left of the wooden house##1
 5. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
 7. the social-worker is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 8. the lawyer is the vegafina-smoker##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is between the townhouse house and the oliveros-smoker##2
10. the alhambra-smoker is the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Transport          | bus         | quad-bike         | snowmobile     | train      |
| Job           | security-guard | social-worker | freelancer    | lawyer     |
| Cigar   | oliveros      | alhambra       | dannemann    | vegafina       |
| House         | farmhouse     | wooden       | townhouse | tower |

