.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, tea, soy-milk, milk
4 different pets are kept: lizard, frog, bird, hamster
City: miami, liverpool, paris, venice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, cycling, sailing
1. the owner of the lizard is between the person who's sport is sailing and the owner of the bird##2
2. the person drinking tea is between the owner of the lizard and the person traveling to venice##2
3. the person traveling to paris is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person traveling to liverpool##2
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the person traveling to paris is the person traveling to paris##1
6. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
8. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage           | soy-milk | tea | 7up  | milk |
| Pet   | frog      | hamster       | lizard     | bird      |
| City   | venice   | liverpool      | paris   | miami   |
| Sport         | cycling   | sailing    | climbing | cricket   |

