There 4 different types of food: peas, avocado, cucumber, lime
House: wooden, craftsman, colonial, palace
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, soccer, handball, badminton
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is the colonial house##1
 3. the person eating avocado is between the colonial house and the person who's sport is handball##2
 4. the person eating cucumber is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 5. the palace house is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 7. the wooden house is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 8. the person eating lime is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the colonial house is the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | fantasy | family  | zombie  |
| Food   | peas       | cucumber   | avocado | lime    |
| House   | wooden   | colonial   | palace | craftsman |
| Sport     | rugby    | badminton   | soccer    | handball  |

