3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the russian##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in july and the colonial house##2
6. the nigerian is the futuristic house##1
7. the american is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
8. the french is on the left of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
