.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, lettuce, spinach, tomato
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, helicopter, motorbike, jet-ski
House: craftsman, wooden, farmhouse, cottage
City: rome, colone, miami, edinburgh
 1. the person eating lettuce is the person driving the motorbike##1
 2. the person eating tomato is the person traveling to miami##1
 3. the person driving the motorbike is the person traveling to colone##1
 4. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 5. the cottage house is the person eating grapefruit##1
 6. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 8. the wooden house is on the far right##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person traveling to rome##2
10. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | tomato        | spinach    | grapefruit | lettuce   |
| Transport           | jet-ski | airplane | helicopter   | motorbike |
| House   | farmhouse         | craftsman       | cottage      | wooden     |
| City         | miami       | edinburgh | rome    | colone  |

