.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, folk, funk
There 4 different types of food: corn, nectarine, onion, plum
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, townhouse, colonial
4 different games are played: domino, scrabble, canasta, whist
 1. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 3. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the colonial house##1
 4. the person eating corn is the fan of gospel##1
 5. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 6. the craftsman house is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 7. the person playing canasta is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
 8. the person playing whist is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2
 9. the person eating plum is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
10. the craftsman house is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | folk    | funk      | electronic |
| Food       | corn        | plum       | onion       | nectarine     |
| House      | townhouse | craftsman | colonial | gothic-revival        |
| Game        | scrabble       | whist     | canasta         | domino           |

