 4. the fan of punk is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
 5. the fan of punk is between the fan of classical and the fan of house##2
 6. the pakistani is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 7. the chaman-smoker is the person eating cucumber##1
 8. the canadian is on the far right##1
 9. the fan of house is the brazilian##1
10. the alhambra-smoker is the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food        | cherry  | cucumber | kale     | carrot     |
| Music-Genre         | house | punk | classical     | country |
| Cigar       | old-henry  | chaman   | alhambra | bongani    |
