 4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1
 5. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
 7. the person who's sport is surfing is the person playing canasta##1
 8. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the fan of r&b and the game-smoker##2
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |       4       |
