5. the fan of folk is the person drinking 7up##1
6. the fan of funk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
7. the musician is on the right of the fan of folk##1
8. the designer is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
9. the electrician is on the right of the designer##1

.:: Answer ::.
